in a lot of pain.

01:07:47.178 --> 01:07:49.613
Aw, sonny.

01:07:53.284 --> 01:07:54.484
No.

01:07:56.287 --> 01:07:57.854
No, I wouldn't!

01:07:57.922 --> 01:08:00.490
I wouldn't, jessie,
I wouldn't.

01:08:00.558 --> 01:08:05.328
Oh, sonny.

