01:10:38.867 --> 01:10:40.800
You see, I'm
terrified of pain.

01:10:40.869 --> 01:10:42.302
Pain hurts me.

01:10:42.370 --> 01:10:44.271
Sonny, what makes you
so convinced

01:10:44.339 --> 01:10:45.805
